{"tid":1877891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】 又有黑心口罩準備流出市面","createTime":"2020-02-13T09:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T04:48:36.000Z","uid":86246,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"1de9afc97aee383b36f203e0e2143447413b7e4c","tid":1877891,"uid":86246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:24:54.000Z","msg":"大家近排除左有單過期印尼口罩、跳蝨口罩之外，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實仲有某個谷嘅谷主有一批4百幾箱口罩運送過黎浸咗水污染咗，有up味</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">數量:400幾盒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家俾左一啲清潔嬸嬸執走哂，疑似谷主將件事講左出黎!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後來好多谷友話點解吾將口罩剪咗先棄置，起初兩公婆系度講四百幾箱點樣剪，又話四百幾箱你剪呀，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後來越多人插就扮野話唔係唔想剪,而係清潔嬸嬸太快手</span></span>，但係講真如果你將啲貨係擺喺自己地方唔係棄置，啲清潔嬸嬸點樣可以執咗你批貨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來我都有加入討論，反而將個post設咗隱藏，啱啱30分鐘前，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲喺自己facebook話人on9，二萬幾個口罩點剪</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家明顯係俾佢地害死，個post又冇公開、冇人知，希望大家幫幫手傳開去，我怕有人唔知俾人買咗就麻煩了!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男:cosplay 攝影師 Facebook acc: Azusa Li<br />\n中文名:李洛軒 Li Lok Hin<br />\n**身份證上非香港人&rsquo;Lee&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n女:cosplay 愛好者 Facebook acc: Miyuna Nana<br />\n<br />\n地點:深水埗<br />\n口罩產地:印尼<br />\n口罩品牌:各種都有 <br />\nlink :<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1094495067293073/permalink/2769508373125059/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1094495067293073%2Fpermalink%2F2769508373125059%2F&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebSNFMfcM